{"tid":1544041,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"滿手鮮血，行街恤髮 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T12:03:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb1f04e0fe35d43e46bd23b51cd68dd6108a20a","tid":1544041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190905/20762125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762125&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=6f1c6977\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762125&h=9986c491\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190905/20762125</a><br />\n<br />\n滿手鮮血，行街恤髮 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190905/large/1567579696_4a13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190905%2Flarge%2F1567579696_4a13.jpg&h=929ccc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭司馬昭之心，數度有意無意讓「路透社」披露閉門會議錄音──「洩露國家機密」（一切都是中央決策），目的為了卸膊自保。<br />\n<br />\n為香港引來如此「浩劫」是「不可原諒」的禍首，聲稱「如果有選擇，會第一件事辭職」，暗示自己無法辭職，裝無辜、扮哽咽，重演舊戲，但有人相信你嗎？周二又戀棧權位否認辭職之念了。懶理你日後下場，終須自食其果。<br />\n<br />\n政警黑勾結，兇殘暴戾無法無天，才把港人逼上梁上，城破巢傾，摧毀整整一代年輕人，8人輕生，還有8.31太子站黑警（武警公安）暴行，封鎖兩日的地鐵屍殺列車事件，是否有被捕者「失聯」、「失蹤」？生死真相大家都不知道。<br />\n<br />\n卸膊了，只關心今次風波對她的影響是「現時要出去非常困難，我沒有出過街，沒有去過商場，又不能去髮廊。我什麼也不能做，社交媒體會廣傳我的行蹤，如我公開露面，會有大批穿黑衫戴口罩的年輕人等着我。」──至此，港人肯定怒火沖天，人家連命也沒有了，罪孽深重的毒婦只記掛行街和恤髮？你萬死難辭其咎！<br />\n<br />\n幸好9月9日之後，《香港人權及民主法案》在美國國會安排表決，所有遏制香港基本自由的人渣，在美資產被凍結，本人與家屬亦遭拒絕入境。波及高官也禍延領導人&hellip;&hellip;到時，人渣連大灣區也無立錐之地。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n丟了孔子的臉 (馮睎乾)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n警察打人 (邁克)"},{"pid":"75cfd63db329effc63aadce2c543549328c6aa28","tid":1544041,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"又po上一則下一則啲垃圾<br />\n你弱智？"},{"pid":"b1454b5a651e896816c6fd8552b1e91f97c73801","tid":1544041,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}